snippet.title: Johnny Depp ties knot with fiancee Amber Heard - BT
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp ties knot with fiancee Amber Heard 

"The much-awaited nuptials of actors Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have reportedly already happened at their home here. A source confirmed the news of their marriage here on Tuesday.
A bigger wedding celebration is still to come this weekend on Depp's Little Hall's Pond Cay private island in the Bahamas.
"
